sections.heading: regulations; when authorized; powers; manufactured homes; limitation of jurisdiction
sections.text: (1) The county board shall have power: (a) To create a planning commission with the powers and duties set forth in sections 23-114 to 23-114.05, 23-168.01 to 23-168.04, 23-172 to 23-174, 23-174.02, 23-373, and 23-37
